{"BUY":[{"def":"To acquire the ownership of (property) by giving an accepted price or consideration therefor, or by agreeing to do so; to acquire by the payment of a price or value; to purchase; -- opposed to sell.","pos":""},{"def":"To acquire or procure by something given or done in exchange, literally or figuratively; to get, at a cost or sacrifice; to buy pleasure with pain.","pos":""}],"BUYER":[{"def":"One who buys; a purchaser.","pos":""}]}